WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
I cast a light spell to illuminate the area.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:31.000
The light reveals a hidden path.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:36.000
We should follow this path, it might lead us to safety.

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:55.000
Be careful, it could be a trap.

00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:57.000
I sense magic in the air.

00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:59.000
Stay alert, everyone.

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:08.000
I hear footsteps approaching.

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:10.000
Prepare yourselves!
